w will focus on the findings of Steinhoff's investigation into accounting irregularities and the consequences for the company's credit profile. "Should further details of the accounting irregularities put additional pressure on Steinhoff's financial condition, this could lead to further downward pressure on the ratings."Steinhoff shares were trading at R6.25 on the JSE at around 10:30.
